data.name: $FILE_ID
data.comment: {locked} This is the file ID for this localization file. This string value should not be used or translated.

data.name: tooManyComponentsError
data.value: Too many components found for id "{0}".
data.comment: {Locked}An error to show when there are too many component for one id. Used when requesting component by id without a specific version. {0} is the component id.

data.name: deleteComponentLog
data.value: Deleting component "{0}" version "{1}" from the store.
data.comment: {Locked}A log message to show when a component is going to be deleted from the component store. {0} is the component id, {1} is the component version.

data.name: noComponentFoundError
data.comment: {Locked}An error to show when a component for the specified id could not be found. Used when requesting component by id without a specific version. {0} is the component id.

data.name: manifestNotFoundByIdError
data.value: Manifest not found for component id "{0}".
data.comment: {Locked}An error to show when the manifest could not be found. Shows only the id, to use when version is not available. {0} is the component id.

data.name: tooManyManifestsError
data.comment: {Locked}An error to show when there are too many manifests for one id. Used when requesting manifest by id without a specific version. {0} is the number of manifests found, {1} is a comma-separated list of the manifest versions, {2} is the component id.

data.name: tooManyCompatibleVersionsError
data.value: {0} compatible versions ({1}) found for component "{2}" version "{3}".
data.comment: {Locked}An error to show when there are too many compatible versions for one id and version. Used when requesting manifest by id and version. Only one compatible version should be found. {0} is the number of manifests found, {1} is a comma-separated list of the found versions, {2} is the component id, {3} is the component version.
